JUST GET BACK, PLEASE!

00:41.100 --> 00:43.000
WHOA, TAO, THANK GOD.

00:43.200 --> 00:45.700
WOULD YOU PLEASE
TELL THESE PEOPLE

00:45.700 --> 00:48.800
TO CALM DOWN
AND STEP BACK?

00:50.500 --> 00:53.900
CALM DOWN AND STEP BACK!

00:57.100 --> 00:59.600
YOU DON'T SPEAK CHINESE?

00:59.600 --> 01:03.600
NO, I DON'T.
I'M FOURTH-GENICAN.

01:04.099 --> 01:07.800
WELL, YOU ALWAYS SOUND FLUENT
WHEN WE ORDER TAKEOUT!

01:15.400 --> 01:19.000
Clay: WHY OWN A 4x4 IF YOU CAN'T
PERFORM SIDEHILL MANEUVERS

01:19.000 --> 01:20.700
WITHOUT IT STALLING OUT?

01:20.700 --> 01:24.500
NOW, IF YOUR TRUCK HAS A
SQUARE-FLANGED INTAKE MANIFOLD,

01:24.500 --> 01:29.300
YOU'D BE CRAZY NOT TO INSTALL
AN OFF-ROAD CARBURETOR.

01:29.300 --> 01:30.900
Brenda:
MAMA, YOU REALIZE

01:30.900 --> 01:33.800
RESTAURANTS IN LOS ANGELES
SERVE LUNCH, TOO.

01:33.800 --> 01:36.800
AND CHARGE $15
FOR A SANDWICH.

01:36.800 --> 01:38.900
NO.
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

01:44.000 --> 01:46.200
HAVE YOU THOUGHT
ABOUT WHEN YOU AND FRITZ

01:46.200 --> 01:47.200
WILL HAVE THE WEDDING?

01:47.200 --> 01:48.500
OH, FOR HEAVEN SAKES,
MOTHER,

01:48.500 --> 01:52.500
WE HAVEN'T EVEN DECIDED
IF WE <i>WANT</i> A CEREMONY -- AT ALL.

01:55.200 --> 01:59.200
NOW, HONEY, DON'T TAKE THIS
THE WRONG WAY,

01:59.600 --> 02:02.500
BUT IF YOU'RE EVEN THINKING
ABOUT STARTING A FAMILY,

02:02.800 --> 02:04.600
TICKTOCK GOES THE CLOCK.

02:04.600 --> 02:07.100
COME ON, WILLIE RAE.

02:07.100 --> 02:09.100
ONE THING AT A TIME.

02:09.100 --> 02:10.800
I MEAN, THEY'VE GOT TO FIND
A HOUSE FIRST.

02:10.800 --> 02:13.200
THIS PLACE IS NOT BIG ENOUGH
FOR A KID.

02:13.200 --> 02:14.700
WELL, ABOUT THAT...

02:16.800 --> 02:19.900
BRENDA, DON'T TELL ME THAT
YOU TWO ARE GETTING MARRIED

02:19.900 --> 02:21.000
BECAUSE YOU'RE PREGNANT?

02:21.000 --> 02:22.000
NO, MAMA!

02:22.000 --> 02:23.000
WHAT I'M TRYING TO TELL YOU

02:23.000 --> 02:26.100
IS THAT I'M GOING THROUGH
EARLY ONSET MENOPAUSE, OKAY?!

02:26.100 --> 02:30.100
ISN'T THAT JUST --
JUST LOADS BETTER?

02:30.400 --> 02:33.000
MORE COFFEE, ANYONE?

02:38.700 --> 02:39.600
HELLO?

02:40.200 --> 02:41.800
OH, YES, COMMANDER.

02:41.800 --> 02:42.600
OH, NO, NO, NO.

02:42.600 --> 02:46.300
UM, I'M BACK ON ACTIVE DUTY
AS OF YESTERDAY.

02:51.700 --> 02:54.500
THE VICTIM WAS A 33-YEAR-OLD
CHINESE NATIONAL

02:54.500 --> 02:56.200
WITH PERMANENT-RESIDENCE
STATUS.

02:56.200 --> 02:58.700
HER NAME
WAS PING-MEI ZHANG.

02:58.700 --> 03:01.700
SHE OWNED AND OPERATED
EIGHT STARS TOURS,

03:01.700 --> 03:04.800
WHICH, AS YOU CAN SEE,
WAS PRETTY SUCCESSFUL.

03:06.000 --> 03:08.600
SO, PING-MEI --
PING-MEI...

03:08.600 --> 03:10.600
Tao: HER HUSBAND
AND FATHER-IN-LAW ARE WAITING

03:10.600 --> 03:12.400
FOR WHEN YOU
FINISH UP HERE.

03:13.200 --> 03:14.700
LIEUTENANT.
CHIEF.

03:18.500 --> 03:20.500
AND THIS IS A PRIORITY
BECAUSE...?

03:20.500 --> 03:22.100
EIGHT STARS
WAS SHUTTLING AROUND

03:22.100 --> 03:24.400
SEVERAL HIGH-RANKING
COMMUNIST PARTY OFFICIALS

03:24.400 --> 03:26.200
FROM THE MAINLAND.

03:30.800 --> 03:33.600
Tao: PRELIMINARY EXAM
SHOWS THE VICTIM WAS STRUCK

03:33.600 --> 03:34.500
ON THE FRONT OF THE SKULL

03:34.500 --> 03:36.400
WITH AN UNIDENTIFIED
BLUNT OBJECT.

03:36.400 --> 03:37.500
GIVEN HOW SHE FELL,

03:37.500 --> 03:39.900
LOOKS LIKE SHE WAS ON HER KNEES
WHEN SHE GOT HIT.

03:39.900 --> 03:41.700
MAYBE SHE WAS ASKING
FOR MERCY.

03:43.900 --> 03:45.800
OR SHE WAS LOOKING FOR THIS.

03:48.900 --> 03:51.100
LET'S FIND OUT WHAT'S
ON THIS CAMERA, PLEASE.

03:56.200 --> 03:57.600
WHO CALLED THIS IN?

03:57.600 --> 03:59.300
AROUND 5:00 A.M.
THIS MORNING,

03:59.300 --> 04:01.400
PING-MEI'S HUSBAND
AND HER FATHER-IN-LAW --

04:01.400 --> 04:03.500
BOTH, UH,
CHINESE NATIONALS --

04:03.500 --> 04:06.700
THEY ARRIVED TO OPEN UP
THE OFFICE, SERVICE THE BUSES.

04:06.700 --> 04:09.900
HUSBAND DISCOVERS WIFE'S BODY.
HE CALLS 911.

04:11.000 --> 04:17.074
